{
  "name": "Breath of Wind Gusts",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Icons/Bukijutsu.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You begin to collect and manifest wind release chakra until it laces the striking portion of your weapon. The wind release chakra begins to spiral around the user's weapon creating whipping torrents of wind. You spin sideways, rotating your body in an uppercut motion, allowing the wind Release to create a massive and powerful arcing slash.</p><p>All creatures of your choice in a 5-foot wide, 60-foot line originating from you must make a Dexterity saving throw, taking your [weapons damage] + 4d6 wind damage and 1 ranks of bleeding on a failed save or half as much and no ranks of lacerated on a success.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above B-Rank increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and the damage by 1d6.</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
